 2001 ha registrato su video 555 interviste a testimoni che hanno ricordato le loro esperienze durante la seconda guerra mondiale."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1145106", "itemLabel": "histoire", "dhsid": "027838", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "", "articlede": "", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "Recorded history", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recorded_history", "instanceof": "", "instanceofLabel": "", "gndid": ""}, {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q209815", "itemLabel": "tradition orale", "dhsid": "027838", "namefr": "Tradition orale", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tradition_orale", "namede": "M\u00fcndliche \u00dcberlieferung", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C3%BCndliche_%C3%9Cberlieferung", "nameit": "Tradizione orale", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tradizione_orale", "nameen": "Oral tradition", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oral_tradition", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q38786485", "instanceofLabel": "mode de communication", "gndid": "4040600-3"}, {"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q42412341", "itemLabel": "tradition \u00e9crite", "dhsid": "027838", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "Schriftliche \u00dcberlieferung", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schriftliche_%C3%9Cberlieferung", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q38786485", "instanceofLabel": "mode de communication", "gndid": ""}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q209815", "wikipedia_page_title": "Tradizione orale", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/027838/2012-11-26"}